[
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗摩訶目連遊四衢經",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a18_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "後漢外國三藏康孟詳譯",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a20_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聞如是：一時，釋氏舍夷阿摩勒藥樹園。爾時，",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者舍利弗、摩訶目乾連比丘，遊行諸國經歷一年，與大比丘眾俱，比丘五百，還至藥樹，欲見世尊。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a24_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是等來還，比丘眾多各共語言，各各著衣持鉢，其聲高大音響暢逸。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a25_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛以預知，問賢者阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a26_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「此何比丘？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a26_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "揚大音聲其響洋逸，如捕魚師揚聲驗逸？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a27_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯然世尊！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860a28_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗、目乾連，遊止諸國經歷一載，大比丘眾五百人俱至於藥樹，見諸比丘各各談語，著衣持鉢，語言聲高音響暢溢。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b02_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛語阿難：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b03_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「勿令比丘來至吾許。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b03_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」阿難白佛：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b03_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯然。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b04_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」奉命從座起，稽首佛足繞佛三匝而退，往詣舍利弗、目連比丘所，言語敘閙却住一面，謂賢者舍利弗、目連：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b06_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「令餘比丘勿詣佛所，世尊有教。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」舍利弗、目連聞阿難言，即從坐起往詣佛所，稽首足下繞佛三匝，速去衣鉢，出詣藥樹與比丘眾俱。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b09_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，釋種諸優婆塞，悉聚會有所講一義，遙見舍利弗、大目連，比丘眾俱，著衣持鉢，晝日平旦詣於藥樹下，「五百比丘眾俱，吾等寧可往問起居。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b13_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，諸釋種優婆塞眾，即起速往詣舍利弗目連所，前稽首足下却住一面。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "時，諸清信士問舍利弗、目連：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b15_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「何故著衣持鉢，晝日而往於藥樹間？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b16_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」舍利弗、目連答釋種清信士：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b17_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「吾等遊諸國來還詣比丘眾，皆以疲倦今此露住。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b18_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」諸清信士答曰：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b18_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯諸賢者！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b18_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "吾等於斯具足施坐然燈為明，唯願屈神及比丘眾，若謂佛者乃可捨退。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b20_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」賢者舍利弗、大目乾連，嘿然可之，尋往所施坐其床榻，則入其室與眾僧俱坐。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "爾時，釋種諸清信士，往詣佛所稽首足下叉手白佛：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b24_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等請求世尊求哀安住，唯然大聖！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b24_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "信比丘眾。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b25_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於彼比丘諸漏盡者，已得羅漢所作已辦，吾不懷疑。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b26_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此等比丘亦不猶豫，其有比丘幼小新學初出家者，入是法律未久，其心移易或能變異，譬如世間暴水卒來無所遮隔。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是世尊！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860b29_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "新學比丘初出家者，入是法律未久，其心移易或能變異，不覲大聖恐改志行。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c02_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」於時梵天忽然來下，即住佛前叉手白言：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c03_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「我等請求世尊，求哀安住，唯然大聖！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c04_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "信比丘眾。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c04_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c04_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於眾比丘諸漏盡者，已得羅漢所作已辦，吾不疑。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c05_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此等比丘亦不猶豫，其有比丘幼小新學初出家者，入是法律未久，其心移易或能變異。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c07_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛即然可梵天王。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c08_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "賢者摩訶目乾連，天眼徹視遙見佛心可之，請求覩大聖德。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c09_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如大枰閣若大講堂，淨潔塗治開諸軒窓，日東初出入于軒窓光照西壁，賢者目連天眼徹視，遙見世尊相好巍巍，時目乾連尋語比丘眾：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c12_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「諸賢者！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c12_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當起著衣持鉢，梵天請求諸幼小各詣。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c13_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」比丘曰：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c13_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「唯當受教。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c14_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」速正衣服，隨舍利弗、大目連等往詣佛所，稽首足下退坐一面。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c15_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於時，世尊告舍利弗：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c16_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「吾亦前世供比丘眾，於心云何？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c16_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」舍利弗，心自念言：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c17_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「世尊宿世供比丘眾，於此大聖，比丘質朴，於求望知節行安常志精進，佛天中天則為法王，調諸不調然當受教，諸比丘眾舉動輕飄，今日大聖慈愍眾僧。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c20_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c20_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「善哉善哉！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c20_22",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c21_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正當念此蠲除惡念。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c21_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c21_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰為比丘眾去諸重擔？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c22_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯如來耳無所不住，及舍利弗、摩訶目乾連。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c23_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」時，佛告大目連曰：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c24_8",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「於心云何？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c24_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰敬比丘眾？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c24_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "誰制比丘眾？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c25_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」我心念言：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c25_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「今佛世尊敬制比丘眾，唯然大聖！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c26_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "此比丘眾或有質朴少求知足，或不能者，自謂行安精進無懈，如來法王自應當然，吾亦如是。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c28_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「且止，勿有斯念！",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c28_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當更異念。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於是目連，誰能堪任去諸重擔？",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0860c29_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "唯如來耳，及舍利弗、大目乾連。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0861a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「以信渡流氾，　　無放逸為船，",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0861a02_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "聖諦濟苦患，　　智慧究竟渡。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0861a03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛分別是語時，六十比丘漏盡意解，無數比丘遠塵離垢，諸法眼生。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0861a05_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "佛說如是，諸比丘、清信士、天、龍、鬼神，莫不歡喜。",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0861a06_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "舍利弗摩訶目連遊四衢經",
        "from": "T02n0137_001:0861a07_100",
        "context_with_next_sentence": false
    }
]